
## PROJECT OVERVIEW

Band Brain Hub: A collaborative web application for band management.  Focus on rapid deployment, excellent UX/UI, and seamless mobile experience.  Real-time synchronization and offline support are critical.

## CODE STYLE

Adhere to standard TypeScript and React best practices.  Maintain consistency in styling using Tailwind CSS.

## FOLDER ORGANIZATION

(To be defined based on project evolution)

## TECH STACK

- React
- TypeScript
- Supabase
- shadcn/ui
- Tailwind CSS
- IndexedDB (for offline support)


## PROJECT-SPECIFIC STANDARDS

- Prioritize intuitive UX/UI design, considering the needs of non-technical band members.
- All components must integrate with the Supabase database.
- Real-time updates are mandatory using Supabase subscriptions.
- Offline functionality is required using IndexedDB or a similar solution.
- Comprehensive error handling and loading states are essential.


